org.phantomapi.world

Class PE

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.potion.PotionEffect
      • org.phantomapi.world.PE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable

    public class PE
extends org.bukkit.potion.PotionEffect
    Fast potion effects like this

    PE.HEAL.d(40).a(2).c(); >> PotionEffect (a = amp; d = dur; c = create)
    PE.HEAL.d(40).a(2).c(Player p) >> Apply potion effect;
    Author:
    cyberpwn
